Comment: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,ROGER'S RECOLLECTION\NON THEIR WAY BACK FROM THE FISH-MAN ISLAND | Roger's Recollection on their way back from the Fish-Man Island
Comment: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:50.49,Main,,0,0,0,,OFF THE COAST OF THE LAND OF WANO | The Seas around of Wano Country
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oden joined the Roger Pirates,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and sailed across the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.44,Translation Info,,0,0,0,,ロード歴史の本文ポーネグリフ Road Poneglyph, \NRoad Text of History
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...seeking the Road Poneglyphs\Nwhich detailed the location of the last island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Guided by the four Poneglyphs,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:18.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Gol D. Roger finally made \Nit to the last island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:27.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\t(5487,$end,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}People lavishly praised \NRoger's accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Oden.\NWhat did you think of the last island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,My body still burns with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what you said to me\Nwhen we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,"Turn the world upside down," wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You also said, "We were destined to meet."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Is the promise fulfilled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,B-Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain's...! Captain Roger's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,They flashily came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:50.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Redtaro asked Roger\Nwho came back from Laugh Tale something,...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and broke into tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The world went wild\Nover the birth of the King of the Pirates,...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...and the Marine started acting aggressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,The man who attained everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The King of the Pirates, Gold Roger"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Gol D. Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:29.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But being called the King of the Pirates\Nisn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I understand why the World Government\Nwants to cover up your name like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:41.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The world called\Neverything that Roger gained collectively...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:46.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...the great treasure of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.77,Main,,0,0,0,,They don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,But because of your fame,\Neveryone's coming to get you, Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Take down Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Find Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Plunder his treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger has everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking back, it has all been miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,With such a limited life expectancy,\NI can't believe I made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I have nothing but gratitude for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa-whoa-whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you speaking formally like that?!\NDamn you, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make me blush, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on! I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The Roger Pirates are disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Will be born...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:09.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Our ruler will be born...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Another will be born in a distant sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:18.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Even whales are happy to know\Nthat the two rulers will meet again one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We have been waiting for so long, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It will not be long...\NIt is going to work out this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}10 until the birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}15 until growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:49.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}How can you talk so deep under the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, Shyarly,\Nwhen will the Mermaid Princess be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be1}10!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it's telling the truth.\NSomeone will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And that person will surpass us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,We came too early...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The One Piece, huh? \NI wonder who will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I think that will be my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have one in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.03,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:44.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sail towards somewhere where there's no Marine!\NI'll disembark first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys! Take Oden home next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Oden!\NI'm thinking about meeting Whitebeard before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\t(2819,$end,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Do you want Izo to return\Nto the Wano Country, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.80,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,He meshed with the crew of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell him to take care of White-Kichi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\t(714,$end,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:48.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,After some words to Rayleigh,\Nthe longest-serving member known as the Dark King...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Roger left the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:03.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,He received a bundle of medicine\Nfrom the ship's doctor Crocus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:07.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,He was reaching the final \Nstage of his illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:12.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,But just like the farewell of every man,\Nno one cried a single tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,The King of the Pirates' crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:22.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...don't shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's still astonishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Wrecked ships that couldn't \Nenter the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,If you catch a wrong current,...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.90,Main,,0,0,0,,...the ship will be destroyed\Nwithout getting near the Wano Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.78,Main,,0,0,0,,In the past, this isolation \Npolicy had a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But we must open it up\Nbefore "Joy Boy" comes one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That bastard! He's flashily walking away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Be well, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I am not dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:10.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,So we said goodbye smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:13.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Because I will see them again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I missed you all, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,There, Hiyori! Up you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I called you "Father"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've grown so much, Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! I hope all is well with you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,How polite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you be so impolite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You think you deserve politeness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Otoki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Look how popular I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I was neglecting the country for so long.\NI thought I'd be criticized more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank your wife, Toki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She is a very wonderful person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,When she recovered from her illness,\Nshe went down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...to the town and helped citizens every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,She has never acted arrogantly \Nas a Daimyo's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,She labored with everyone\Nand cheerfully shared the stories of your adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Toki-sama and your children are\Nextremely popular in Kuri now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And they kept saying nice things about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,At some point,\Neveryone stopped speaking ill of your selfish behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! Thank you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it!\NWe really love you! Right, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous! I wanna be loved, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiku! I must tell you about Izo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Inu-chan and Neko-chan told me!\NI'm fine as long as he's doing well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nwhat happened to Denjiro and Ashura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't see them a year ago, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ashura became the boss of the yakuza \Nand mountain bandits in Kuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,...to keep them under control!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Denjiro is wandering about,\Nborrowing money and paying it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Neither wrangling bandits\Nor borrowing money sound like comfortable lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:18:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,There is another reason that everyone is happy\Nabout your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I will tell the story from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,After you left, we managed to run the Daimyo-less Kuri\Nwith the citizens' cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how is my father doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Shogun-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,So he wasn't well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What a shame that I couldn't be with him\Nwhen he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The problem is the Shogun-sama's successor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It is hard to understand,\Nbut at your father Sukiyaki-sama's request,...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.31,Main,,0,0,0,,...that Orochi became...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.65,Past,,0,0,0,,{\t(2661,$end,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Please lend me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I got confused by listening to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Orochi is like a little brother to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I only lent him money\Nout of respect for Yasu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,He did not pay me back even a Silver coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:10.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I also learned that Orochi is a \Ndescendant of the Kurozumi Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...that once caused some big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:19.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It seems like Kurozumi Orochi is now sitting as the Shogun\Nas a proxy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I am sure you saw them on your way here,...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...but each region has several weapon factories\Nand people who oversee laborers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,And the men of each region \Nare forced to work there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...earning poverty wages by the Shogun's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is that?!\NWhy does everyone listen to someone like Orochi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:45.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That is because a pirate named Kaido\Nis supporting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,...and he is monstrously strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\NOrochi is doing whatever he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! We tried to attack Orochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No, tell me! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Take Momonosuke-sama and Hiyori-sama\Nout of the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, about half a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:21.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...a man who refused to labor at a weapon factory\Nand his family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...were executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,We could not take any \Nmore of Orochi's cruelty,...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,...and motivated by anger, we \Nmarched into Orochi's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,...in the Flower Capital with \Nkatanas in our hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But we got outsmarted and\NKaido's subordinates arrived at Kuri at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,They invaded this castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,...and we let them attack Momonosuke-sama\Nwho is Kozuki's next heir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...in the line after Oden-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,the enemies were taken down by...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...Kawamatsu and Inuarashi\Nwho stayed to guard the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But the one who saved him\Nfrom their first arrow attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\t(3819,$end,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}...was Toki-sama who threw \Nherself in front of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I am deeply sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Because our reckless action,\NToki-sama seriously injured her leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We put your family members' lives in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me see, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not worry, Oden-san!\NIt is already healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for protecting our child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It must have been hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Oden-san! \NIf you lose your temper over a little thing like this,...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...we will be attacked again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:13.09,Main,,0,0,0,,A... A...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,A little thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Toki, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...have not heard about the \Nstories of my old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Your old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, um, since he was a \Nchild, Oden-sama was known...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...for drinking and fighting, \Nand ended up being arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,He was a rough neck\Nwho everyone in the Flower Capital was afraid of...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand the way Orochi does things!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys! Protect my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:52.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Protect Kuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:11.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oden can't tolerate Orochi's \Nevil acts and becomes furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:15.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With Emma, he aims for nothing less than\Ntaking the Shogun's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When the fate of the Wano Country\Nis about to be turned around,...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...word from the King of the Pirates \Nechoes over the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:26.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and throws the whole world \Ninto rapture and turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Sad News! \NThe Opening of the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
